Core Library 2.0 Design Notes

Zilin Du, Jan 2006

1. list of classes:

  BigInt   -- wrapper of mpz
  BigRat   -- wrapper of mpq

  Double   -- wrapper of machine double, IEEE floating-point number
  Mpfr     -- wrapper of mpfr, extended IEEE floating-point number (weak mode)

  FpFilter -- floating-pointer filter (currently a pair of Double)
  BigFloat -- strong mode of floating-point number (currently a pair of Mpfr)
  IA       -- generic interval arithmetic template class, used by BigFloat 
              and FpFilter
  
  ExprRep  -- internal expression node
  Expr     -- expression
   
